00:18:24,780 --> 00:18:26,300
I'm Tong Huen, a Senior Inspector

301
00:18:26,420 --> 00:18:27,700
from Eastern District Police Station.

302
00:18:28,420 --> 00:18:29,180
Ms. Tong,

303
00:18:29,580 --> 00:18:30,100
hello.

304
00:18:30,500 --> 00:18:31,740
