310
00:18:39,420 --> 00:18:40,460
Do you remember

311
00:18:40,460 --> 00:18:41,780
who gave you

312
00:18:41,780 --> 00:18:42,820
the herbal tea?

313
00:18:43,020 --> 00:18:44,460
I brought it there myself.

314
00:18:44,900 --> 00:18:45,860
Then do you remember

315
00:18:46,100 --> 00:18:47,740
if anyone touched it?

316
00:18:49,180 --> 00:18:50,340
Not really.

317
00:18:50,980 --> 00:18:52,100
There were

318
00:18:52,380 --> 00:18:53,980
