319
00:18:55,420 --> 00:18:56,860
Before you passed out,

320
00:18:57,140 --> 00:18:58,860
who took you to the prayer room?

321
00:18:59,460 --> 00:19:00,500
I remember that.

322
00:19:01,140 --> 00:19:02,020
It was a man.

323
00:19:02,700 --> 00:19:03,700
He was holding me,

324
00:19:04,060 --> 00:19:05,460
and I had a look at him.

325
00:19:05,940 --> 00:19:07,500
Could you help us with the portraiture?

326
00:19:11,740 --> 00:19:12,740
I can try.

327
00:19:13,820 --> 00:19:14,500
Thank you.

